## Purpose
Details the internal structure of GgenMcpServer showing all 16 tools, resources, prompts, completions, and their connections to backend services.

## Key Components
- **ToolRouter**: Routes tool calls to appropriate handlers
- **16 Tools**: Core functionality organized by category (pipeline, examples, validation, orchestration)
- **Resources**: Browseable data about examples (ttl, readme, config)
- **Prompts**: Reusable LLM templates for common workflows
- **Completions**: Argument autocomplete for example names and generators
- **Backend Services**: Core ggen functionality (sync, oxigraph, quality gates, cycle fixer)
